---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import { SITE } from '../consts';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description="Privacy Policy for SavePoint Guides, including cookies, analytics, and advertising."
  canonicalPath="/privacy-policy/"
>
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 py-14">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-white">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-[var(--color-text-muted)]">
      Last updated: March 28, 2026
    </p>

    <div class="prose-guide mt-8">
      <p>
        This Privacy Policy explains how {SITE.title} ("we", "us", or "our") collects, uses, and
        shares information when you visit {SITE.url}.
      </p>

      <h2>Information we collect</h2>
      <p>
        We may collect standard log data such as browser type, pages visited, referring URLs, and
        approximate location derived from IP address. If you subscribe to a newsletter or contact
        form, we collect the information you submit.
      </p>

      <h2>Cookies and analytics</h2>
      <p>
        We may use cookies and similar technologies for analytics (such as Google Analytics) and
        advertising (such as Google AdSense). You can control cookies through your browser settings.
      </p>

      <h2>Advertising partners</h2>
      <p>
        Third-party vendors, including Google, may use cookies to serve ads based on your prior
        visits to this website or other websites. You can opt out of personalized advertising by
        visiting Google Ads Settings.
      </p>

      <h2>Affiliate links</h2>
      <p>
        Outbound affiliate links may use tracking parameters so partners can attribute purchases.
        See our <a href="/affiliate-disclosure/">Affiliate Disclosure</a>.
      </p>

      <h2>Data retention</h2>
      <p>
        We retain information only as long as needed for the purposes described in this policy or
        as required by law.
      </p>

      <h2>Your rights</h2>
      <p>
        Depending on your region, you may have rights to access, correct, or delete personal data.
        Contact us to make a request.
      </p>

      <h2>Changes</h2>
      <p>
        We may update this policy from time to time. Material changes will be posted on this page
        with a revised date.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
